## Usage

```bash
# Run in development
bun run src/cli.ts --help

# Run hello command
bun run src/cli.ts hello World
bun run src/cli.ts hello Alice --greeting "Hi" --loud

# Show config
bun run src/cli.ts config
```

## Effect-ts Features

This template demonstrates:

- **@effect/cli** - Type-safe CLI argument parsing
- **@effect/platform** - Cross-platform abstractions
- **Effect services** - Dependency injection with Context.Tag
- **Layers** - Composable dependency management
- **Effect.gen** - Generator-based effect composition

